Introduction

Laboum currently consists of 4 members: Soyeon, Jinyea, Haein and Solbin. They debuted in August 2014, under Global H Media (NHMedia and NegaNetwork).

On November 3, 2017, it was announced that Yulhee left the band. On September 8, 2021, Yujeong also departed from the group after her contract expired. Following in 2022, the group went on a hiatus.
